    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in absolute showroom condition. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent and supple texture, with zero bolster wear or carpet staining. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records, documenting every fluid flush and scheduled maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of weepage or oxidation. Included in the sale are two original master keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a collector-grade example that drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle.",
